    "description": "这是你作为地牢潜行者公司新员工上班的第一天。作为一名新地牢潜行者，你的任务是清理废弃的地牢，确保冒险者的安全。在这款类似扫雷的解谜游戏中，利用你的智慧和一些可靠的物品，清除所有陷阱。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >测试你的智慧</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844790/extras/b79ef9fb3b89ef2bbdb8fabcfe4195e4.poster.avif?t=1770406840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844790/extras/b79ef9fb3b89ef2bbdb8fabcfe4195e4.webm?t=1770406840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844790/extras/b79ef9fb3b89ef2bbdb8fabcfe4195e4.mp4?t=1770406840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>需要为近十几种不同类型的房间解除武装，每个房间都有其独特的状况、怪癖和逻辑。随着游戏的发展，你的任务会变得越来越复杂且难以破解。尝试次数有限，需谨慎选择，否则你的任务将最终以失败告终。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >供你使用的武器库</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844790/extras/fc50695c82d9f3f1c49e912d0b9e3015.poster.avif?t=1770406840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844790/extras/fc50695c82d9f3f1c49e912d0b9e3015.webm?t=1770406840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844790/extras/fc50695c82d9f3f1c49e912d0b9e3015.mp4?t=1770406840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>随着不断探索并穿过已清除的地牢，你可能会发现一些强大的物品来帮助你完成这个旅程。 有些物品可以帮助你补救错误，有些可能会赋予你发现重要线索的能力，有些则会给带来你额外的财富。明智地选择，因为你一次只能携带有限的物品。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地牢布局各异</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844790/extras/d4b41abadb92ecfce06a7b0e677f9582.poster.avif?t=1770406840\" width=600 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844790/extras/d4b41abadb92ecfce06a7b0e677f9582.webm?t=1770406840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1844790/extras/d4b41abadb92ecfce06a7b0e677f9582.mp4?t=1770406840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>地牢布局各异意味着每次探索皆不同，确保在你逐级通关时可享受无数小时娱乐。",
